Detailed Description

external definitions for PILAR.

SYNOPSIS

DESCRIPTION Contains all the external definitions for the different modules of the Protein Identification and Library Access Resource. Include it for making all the needed functions globally available.

CAVEATS This is dynamically modified as the project is being built up.

FILES PORTABLE.H P_GLOBALS.C P_PROTEIN.C P_DESCRIPTOR.C P_PARSER.C P_DBANK.C P_INIT.C P_REGION.C P_VALUES.C P_UTILS.C P_LIST.C P_DLIST.C P_STACK.C P_QUEUE.C P_SORT.C

Note:
Some definitions may be never be used. They are there just for historical reasons.
See also:
It may be worth having a look to the mentioned files to get more information about these routines.
